 time talking\nto me looking like that.<PageBreak>Listen, your fashion sense—or lack of\nfashion sense—is your own, but...<PageBreak>I simply can NOT be guilty by association\nof the fashion crimes you're committing\nright now."},{"id":46947,"index":255,"key":"FashionNpcNakedTalk_F_002","CNzh":"<unk[3:0:10]><unk[4:0:12 83 97 100 95 48 49]>不好意思……<PageBreak>我不是很想\n跟赤身裸体的人说话……\n告辞……","TWzh":"<unk[3:0:10]><unk[4:0:12 83 97 100 95 48 49]>對不起……<PageBreak>我實在不是很想跟你這種\n不穿衣服的人說話……\n請恕我先告辭了……","JPja":"<unk[3:0:10]><unk[4:0:12 83 97 100 95 48 49]>ごめんなさい…<PageBreak><Ruby={2:6}わたし>私 お<Ruby={4:8}ようふく>洋服を<Ruby={2:2}き>着ていないような<Ruby={2:4}ひと>人とは\nちょっとお<Ruby={2:4}はな>話しする<Ruby={2:2}き>気になれないので…\n<Ruby={4:8}しつれい>失礼しますね…","USen":"<unk[3:0:10]><unk[4:0:12 83 97 100 95 48 49]>Sorry...<PageBreak>I don't think you and I will have a\nlot in common if you're wearing so\nlittle clothing.\nSo, if you'll excuse me..."},{"id":46948,"index":256,"key":"FashionNpcNakedTalk_M_001","CNzh":"<unk[3:0:7]>……对不起，\n我不希望别人也把我当成可疑的家伙。\n能不能麻烦你起码穿件衣服或者裤子，\n再来和我说话呢……","TWzh":"<unk[3:0:7]>……抱歉。\n我可不想被認為是可疑人物的同伴。\n你有什麼話想說的話，\n至少請你先穿個上衣或褲子吧……","JPja":"<unk[3:0:7]>……<Ruby={2:4}わる>悪い\nこっちまで <Ruby={6:10}ふしんしゃ>不審者に<Ruby={2:2}み>見られるのは<Ruby={2:4}いや>嫌だから\nせめて<Ruby={4:6}うわぎ>上着かズボンを <Ruby={2:2}み>身に<Ruby={2:2}つ>着けてから\n<Ruby={2:4}はな>話しかけてもらえるかな…","USen":"<unk[3:0:7]>Hey, whoa!<unk[5:1]> I'm a free spirit too, but...<PageBreak>You have to put on a shirt or some\ntrousers before you talk to me!"},{"id":46949,"index":257,"key":"FashionNpcNakedTalk_M_002","CNzh":"<unk[3:0:4]><unk[4:0:12 78 111 116 105 99 101]>喂喂！ <unk[5:1]>\n别穿成那副样子跟我说话。\n我可不想让别人以为\n自己跟不穿衣服四处乱跑的人认识！\n我不指望你打扮得多时尚，\n起码穿件衣服再来跟我说话吧！","TWzh":"<unk[3:0:4]><unk[4:0:12 78 111 116 105 99 101]>喂喂喂！<unk[5:1]>\n不要穿成那樣跟我搭話！\n我可不想被人認為\n跟不穿服裝到處亂晃的傢伙認識！\n我不求你穿得時髦，\n但至少隨便穿個服裝吧。","JPja":"<unk[3:0:4]><unk[4:0:12 78 111 116 105 99 101]>おいおい！ <unk[5:1]>\nそんな<Ruby={4:8}かっこう>恰好で <Ruby={2:4}はな>話しかけんじゃねぇよ\nハダカでうろつくヤツと\n<Ruby={2:2}し>知り<Ruby={2:2}あ>合いだと <Ruby={2:4}おも>思われるのはゴメンだ！\nオシャレしろとまでは <Ruby={2:2}い>言わんが\nせめて<Ruby={2:4}なに>何か <Ruby={2:4}ふく>服を<Ruby={2:2}き>着て<Ruby={2:2}こ>来いよな","USen":"<unk[3:0:4]><unk[4:0:12 78 111 116 105 99 101]>Nope, nope, nope.<unk[5:1]> Don't you come talk to\nme looking like that. I can't be seen with\nsomeone who cares so little for clothing.\nI'm not saying you have to dress fancy,\nbut at least put on a shirt or some\ntrousers, you know?"},{"id":46950,"index":258,"key":"NpcBalloon_PouchFull","CNzh":"这谢礼……","TWzh":"謝禮是……","JPja":"お<Ruby={2:4}れい>礼を…","USen":"Your reward..."},{"id":46951,"index":259,"key":"AncientDoctor_Terror_01","CNzh":"嗯哼？","TWzh":"嗯哼？","JPja":"ハハン？","USen":"Hm?"},{"id":46952,"index":260,"key":"AncientDoctor_Terror_02","CNzh":"What！？","TWzh":"What！？","JPja":"ホワッツ！？","USen":"What?!"},{"id":46953,"index":261,"key":"AncientDoctor_Terror_03","CNzh":"Oh my God！","TWzh":"Oh my God！","JPja":"オーマイガッ！","USen":"Goodness gracious!"},{"id":46954,"index":262,"key":"Npc_HatenoVillage019_SisterA_Terror_01","CNzh":"嗒！？","TWzh":"噠！？","JPja":"ダまっ！？","USen":"Wha?!"},{"id":46955,"index":263,"key":"Npc_HatenoVillage019_SisterA_Terror_02","CNzh":"住手嗒说！","TWzh":"住手噠說！","JPja":"やめるダます！","USen":"Stop it!"},{"id":46956,"index":264,"key":"Npc_HatenoVillage019_SisterA_Terror_03","CNzh":"什么嗒说！？","TWzh":"什麼噠說！？","JPja":"なんダます！？","USen":"What's this?!"},{"id":46957,"index":265,"key":"Npc_HatenoVillage019_SisterA_Terror_04","CNzh":"危险嗒说！","TWzh":"危險噠說！","JPja":"<Ruby={2:4}あぶ>危ないダます！","USen":"That's dangerous!"},{"id":46958,"index":266,"key":"HatenoVillage032_Terror_01","CNzh":"什么东西？","TWzh":"討厭！怎麼回事？","JPja":"ヤだ <Ruby={2:4}なに>何？","USen":"Hey, whoa! What is that?"},{"id":46959,"index":267,"key":"HatenoVillage032_Terror_02","CNzh":"多危险啊！","TWzh":"很危險啦！","JPja":"<Ruby={2:4}あぶ>危ないじゃない！","USen":"That is NOT safe!"},{"id":46960,"index":268,"key":"HatenoVillage032_Terror_03","CNzh":"喂！","TWzh":"等等！","JPja":"ちょっ！","USen":"Hey now!"},{"id":46961,"index":269,"key":"HatenoVillage032_Terror_04","CNzh":"不要！","TWzh":"住手！","JPja":"ヤめっ","USen":"NO, thank y